/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a high vantage point, providing a bird's eye view of the scene below. The street is lined with trees, their leaves a vibrant green against the backdrop of the clear blue sky. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the street, their facades bathed in sunlight. Cars of different colors are parked along the sides of the street, adding a splash of color to the scene. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the sky, a common sight in urban landscapes. The image is bathed in the bright sunlight typical of a Beijing day, casting sharp shadows and highlighting the textures of the buildings and trees.
